channel.title: [Delta 317] Adding Korasi, Server Freezes on Startup
channel.description:
I was adding the Korasi to my server, using a tutorial [u][b]designed for 317's[/b][/u]. Everything so far succeeded, except when I run the server and log into my account, the screen is black, with all the interfaces, and saying loading please wait in the top right corner. I waited about 25 minutes, and it was still the same. What could be the problem?
[b]- Thanks, Excel4[/b]
